StyledListCellRenderer.UIResource
public class StyledListCellRenderer
extends StyledLabel
implements javax.swing.ListCellRenderer, java.io.Serializable

A list cell renderer based on StyledLabel. To use it, you should make your cell renderer extending this one and override customizeStyledLabel(javax.swing.JList,Object,int,boolean,boolean) method. If your overridden method, you can call setStyleRange() or setStyleRanges() based on the item value, if it is leaf etc information.
